# Floating Day Timeblock

A floating day timeline widget for SilverBullet with editable categories, day/week views, drag-to-reschedule, and full two-way page sync.

## Config

```lua
config.set("FloatingTimeblock", {
  journalPathPattern = '00 Journal/#year#/#month#-#monthname#/#year#-#month#-#day#'
})
```

Categories are managed directly from the widget (stored in clientStore). On first use with config-based categories, they are auto-migrated.

